            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Fabullius Macer optio classis <expan><abbr>praetor</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> Misenatium III <lb n="2"/>Tigride emit puerum natione Transfluminianum <lb n="3"/>nomine Abban quem Eutychen sive quo alio nomine <lb n="4"/>vocatur annorum circiter septem pretio denariorum <lb n="5"/>ducentorum et capitulario portitorio de <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Iulio <lb n="6"/>Prisco milite classis eiusdem et triere eadem eum pue<lb break="no" n="7"/>rum sanum esse ex edicto et si quis eum puerum <lb n="8"/>partemve quam eius evicerit simplam pecuniam <lb n="9"/>sine denuntiatione recte dare stipulatus est Fabul<lb break="no" n="10"/>lius Macer spopondit <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Iulius Priscus id fide sua <lb n="11"/>et auctoritate esse iussit <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Antiochus mani<lb break="no" n="12"/>pularius III Virtute <lb n="13"/>eosque denarios ducentos qui <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>cripti</ex></expan> sunt probos recte <lb n="14"/>numeratos accepisse et habere dixit <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Iulius Priscus <lb n="15"/>venditor a <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Fabullio Macro emptore et tradedisse <note>sic</note> ei <lb n="16"/>mancipium <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptum</ex></expan> Eutychen bonis condicionibus <lb n="17"/>actum Seleuciae Pieriae in castris in hibernis vexilla<lb break="no" n="18"/>tionis <expan><abbr>clas</abbr><ex>sis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetoriae</ex></expan> Misenatium VIIII <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Iunias <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Servilio <lb n="19"/>Pudente et <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> Fufidio Pollione co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="20"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Iulius Priscus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> III Tigride vendedi <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Fabullio Macro optioni <lb n="21"/>III eadem puerum meum Abbam quem et Eutychen et re<lb break="no" n="22"/>cepi pretium denarios ducentos ita ut <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptum</ex></expan> est <lb n="23"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <expan><abbr>Titianus</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> suboptio III Libero Patre et ipse rogatus pro <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Iulio Antihoco <note>sic</note> manipulario III Virtute qui negavit se lit<expan><ex>t</ex><abbr>eras</abbr></expan> <lb n="24"/>scire eum spondere et fide suam et auctoritate esse Abbam cuen <note>sic</note> ed <note>sic</note> Eutychen puerum ed <note>sic</note> pretium eius denarios ducentos <lb n="25"/>ita ut <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <surplus>S</surplus> scr<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>ptum est <lb n="26"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Arruntius Valens suboptio III Salute signavi <lb n="27"/><expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Isidorus |(centurio) III Providentia signavi <lb n="28"/><expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Demetrius bucinator pri<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>cipalis III Virtute signavi
